item.title: Alpha-beta Pruning
item.description: Search algorithm that decreases the number of gate states to evaluate in [[Braitenberg vehicles|Braitenberg vehicles]] in the game tree. Stopping condition: It does not evaluate further when it realizes that there is already an existing better alternative.
